data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM HOME, WHERE COMFORT AND ELEGANCE BLEND SEAMLESSLY!  This 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem is a true masterpiece. Featuring a Great Room with cathedral ceilings, a magnificent picture window providing a breathtaking view of the tranquil pond and serene wooded backdrop, and brick-to-mantle fireplace adding warmth and character. In the heart of the home, the spacious kitchen has new appliances including a range/oven and dishwasher, updated in August 2022, a corner window, tile backsplash adding a modern touch, and breakfast bar making this space perfect for meals and gatherings. The Kitchen Nook features vaulted ceilings and a cute plant ledge, leading out to the Sunroom. The spacious primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet, nice ensuite, and gorgeous view of the pond and wooded scenery. This split bedroom home features 2 additional, nice sized bedrooms with large closets. The sunroom is a haven of natural light, featuring a cathedral ceiling, ceiling fan,  with big windows framing the picturesque views of the pond and woods. For added convenience, the laundry room features wall cabinets, providing extra storage for your needs. You will appreciate the oversized 2-car garage, complete with floored attic, offering plenty of space for your vehicles, and extra storage. This home has been updated with NEW light fixtures, interior completely painted including closets and trim in 2022. NEW gas forced air furnace and central air in 2022, as well as a new sliding glass patio door in 2022. This home is the essence of comfort, style, and practicality, with every feature you desire. IMMACULATE, MOVE IN READY! YOU DONT HAVE TO LIFT A FINGER! YOUR DREAM HOME AWAITS YOU! DON'T WAIT, IT WILL BE GONE BEFORE YOU KNOW IT!
